data.description: 2 homes on one lot! A private gem. Peaceful and serene, privately enclosed by beautiful and mature landscaping this property is sure to delight. Fenced and cross fenced with horse set-up with 2 stalls, tack room, arena, pastures, and other out buildings. Beautiful mature landscape all throughout add to your enjoyment.Plenty of open space to add shop, barn or both. With a little imagination this property will provide great opportunities for relaxation and enjoyment. Formally appraised at $530,000, both homes have a new roof just 2 years old. Call now.
